// Single-stream fix emission test. The Cryptol `xs = [True] # xs` lowers
// to a SAWCore `fix (Stream Bool) ...`; the Lean backend should translate
// it through the generic proof-carrying fix path rather than a structural
// helper selected by a Haskell recognizer.

write_lean_cryptol_module
  "RecOnes.cry"
  "test_cryptol_module_rec_ones.module.lean" [] [];
